{"tid":1024893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港渣馬真係極其on9嘅一件事","createTime":"2019-02-17T02:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T04:06:38.000Z","uid":236262,"like":30,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4553fa344746dfd5dee79222cce7d7e59e5e07cd","tid":1024893,"uid":236262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"安排混亂，報名程序不在講，現場嘅支援亦近乎零，攪到年年怨聲載道。但香港某嘅參加者又係on撚79，本身間中跑兩三K post上Facebook ig就當自己係跑手，去到現場掛住影相打卡唔熱身，阻撚住曬，跑唔到又夾硬嚟，去到終點跪低暈低嘅一地都係。<br />\n<br />\n年年都係咁，根本唔可以叫做一件體壇盛事，安排配套同部份參加者亦唔尊重馬拉松比賽，執柒咗佢啦DLLM"},{"pid":"df517383015f080f46a69352df2ef74f1b6ed52c","tid":1024893,"uid":236262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"睇到眼火爆"},{"pid":"70c0bb32b8eeea39405cb8a6d4fa0fd0365f1d90","tid":1024893,"uid":236262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:21:58.000Z","msg":"其他地方嘅馬拉松唔可以話好好多，但起碼叫做安排妥當。"},{"pid":"62c347afd21babc4101c8f9f11615344e887de9d","tid":1024893,"uid":61018,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"渣馬係國際打咭賽事<br />\n身為香港人係有義務力爭勝利"},{"pid":"0938fab2de383249562d9ac9d7606c1b3a69117c","tid":1024893,"uid":78791,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f58915bb0edfebe2cede661c4e213945b3af1c67","tid":1024893,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"屌，汀九橋仲封緊，見一堆車入左出唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb54fb3cc4027fa57cbfbf7572bc5f4e850a39e","tid":1024893,"uid":236262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62c347afd21babc4101c8f9f11615344e887de9d","tid":1024893,"uid":61018,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"渣馬係國際打咭賽事<br />\n身為香港人係有義務力爭勝利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"係，我同意。<